      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-exe-liv-ope          .
           move      spaces               to   w-exe-cod-ubi          .
______*    move      spaces               to   w-exe-cod-ubi          .




      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
