           move      02                   to   w-cgi-str-num          .
           perform   ope-prm-inp-000      thru ope-prm-inp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura della variabile di environment          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "I2"                 to   o-ope                  .
           move      "POST"               to   o-com                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
