      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EX"                 to   w-cgi-tip-ope          .
           perform   ope-prm-inp-000      thru ope-prm-inp-999        .
       ext-prm-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Regolarizzazioni                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Password utente                             *
      *                  *                                             *
