      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "INSERIRE UNA PASSWORD VALIDA"
                                          to   w-exe-err-msg          .
           move      "msg_red"            to   w-exe-cla-msg          .
           perform   err-msg-htm-000      thru err-msg-htm-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione password                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-exe-pwd-ute          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A input                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-cph-lv0-180.
       exe-cph-lv0-140.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se record trovato                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
