      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-exe-pwd-ute        not  = spaces        and
                     w-exe-pwd-ute        not  = w-ute-pwd-ute
                     go to exe-cph-lv0-150.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se test superato: a livello successivo      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "1"                  to   w-exe-liv-ope          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Oltre                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-cph-lv0-900.
       exe-cph-lv0-150.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
